snippet.title: ROGUE soldier saves EARTH against CYBORG INVASION - movie recap
snippet.description:
Movie: Revolt (2017)
Brief commentary and analysis:
Soldiers are already brave enough to take on the task of protecting their countries against invaders from foreign countries. But in this movie "Revolt" Bo a soldier from the US is handpicked by the cyborgs that have invaded the earth to be their bait to catch innocent people. When Bo learns about this, he does his best to use this capability against the cyborgs and defeat them.
